rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hiyokkoo doesn't want to salvage... mo. I'm
still a beginner no matter how much time
passes, and it's not fun at all... mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You think so? If you find something
good, you get money, right?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0003
rows.name:
And if you find a treasure you've
never seen before, don't you get
curious about its origins?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Sometimes you get chased by
scary monsters, but I think
the excitement is stronger...

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0005
rows.name:
For me, the fear is stronger,
mo... Do you know the annual
death toll for salvagers, mo?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Let's see... About
twenty people, maybe?

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0007
rows.name:
It's 360 people a year, mo! That's
almost the same number of Nopon who die
from eating poisonous mushrooms, mo!

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Maybe we should be dealing with
the poisonous mushrooms first...

rows.label: tlk42410111_01_msg0009
rows.name:
Ah... I want to quit this
dangerous job soon... mo.
